### 2. COURSE STRUCTURE & CONTENT MANAGEMENT

**Hierarchical Structure:**
```
Course
  ├── Modules (Sections)
  │   ├── Lessons
  │   │   ├── Content (Video, Text, Code, Quiz)
  │   │   ├── Resources (PDFs, Links)
  │   │   └── Exercises (Interactive)
  │   └── Module Quiz
  └── Final Assessment
```

**Database Schema:**
```prisma
model Course {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  title       String
  slug        String   @unique
  description String   @db.Text
  thumbnail   String?
  level       Level    @default(BEGINNER)
  published   Boolean  @default(false)
  modules     Module[]
  enrollments Enrollment[]
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt
}

model Module {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  courseId    String
  course      Course   @relation(fields: [courseId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  title       String
  order       Int
  lessons     Lesson[]
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
}

model Lesson {
  id          String       @id @default(cuid())
  moduleId    String
  module      Module       @relation(fields: [moduleId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  title       String
  order       Int
  type        LessonType
  content     Json         // Flexible content structure
  duration    Int?         // in minutes
  resources   Resource[]
  progress    Progress[]
  createdAt   DateTime     @default(now())
}

enum LessonType {
  VIDEO
  TEXT
  CODE
  QUIZ
  INTERACTIVE
}

model Resource {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  lessonId  String
  lesson    Lesson   @relation(fields: [lessonId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  title     String
  type      ResourceType
  url       String
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}

enum ResourceType {
  PDF
  LINK
  CODE_SNIPPET
  SLIDE
}
```

**Content Types:**
1. **Video Lessons**: HLS streaming, playback speed control, captions
2. **Text Content**: MDX with syntax highlighting, embedded components
3. **Code Exercises**: Monaco Editor with test cases, auto-grading
4. **Quizzes**: Multiple choice, code output prediction, fill-in-blank
5. **Interactive Demos**: Live coding sandboxes, visualizations

