### 5. PROGRESSIVE LEARNING PATHS

**Requirements:**
- Prerequisite system (unlock lessons sequentially)
- Skill trees / learning roadmaps
- Personalized recommendations
- Adaptive difficulty

**Database Schema:**
```prisma
model LearningPath {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  title       String
  description String
  courses     CourseInPath[]
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
}

model CourseInPath {
  id            String       @id @default(cuid())
  pathId        String
  path          LearningPath @relation(fields: [pathId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  courseId      String
  order         Int
  prerequisites String[]     // Array of course IDs
}
```

